------------------------------------------------

Description
-----------
Pol-IP is a complete traffic control for a Linux NAT Box

polipd is a daemon that config the kernel and mantain a statics 
services for multiplataform clients.

The daemon read the config from /etc/polip.conf

To create the config file you can use polipconfig. It is a 
simple wizard made with gnewt.

try

polip.sourceforge.net

